commits.message: Fix inventory sync script: convert from ES modules to CommonJS

Add middleware for authentication and refactor layout components

- Introduced a new middleware to handle authentication checks for protected routes, redirecting unauthenticated users to the login page.
- Refactored the DashboardLayout component by removing server-side authentication logic and simplifying the structure.
- Updated the App component to manage public and private routes more effectively.
- Removed the Home page as it was redundant with the new routing logic.
- Enhanced the login page by streamlining the redirection process after successful login.
